msgid "Using OpenOffice.org Writer"
msgstr "使用 OpenOffice Writer"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:209(title)
msgid "Key Features of OpenOffice.org Writer"
msgstr "OpenOffice.org Writer 的主要特性"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:211(para)
msgid ""
"You may already be familiar with many of the features of this application so "
"only a few of them are included here."
msgstr ""
"或许你对 OpenOffice 办公套件的特性已经有了不少了解 "
"所以这里只介绍它的一部分特性。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:215(title)
msgid "Writing"
msgstr "写作"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:223(para)
msgid ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">Spellchecker:</emphasis> The spellchecker feature "
"facilitates error-free writing by enabling you to check your entire "
"document, including the header, footer, index entries and footnotes, for "
"spelling errors. It even allows you to identify a misspelled word from a "
"specific selection of the document, lists suggested words for replacing the "
"misspelled word and provides you the option to add a new word to the "
"existing user dictionary."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">拼写检查:</emphasis> 拼写检查功能 "
"使你能够在包括文件头尾，目录和脚注在内的整个文件中"
"找出拼写错误，从而确保你的文档在拼写上准确无误"
"它甚至可以使你找出特定文档部分中拼错的词"
"并且列出所有可能的正确单词来替代被拼错的词"
"同时，你也可以自定义用户词典"
"向里面添加新的单词"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:234(para)
msgid ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">Thesaurus:</emphasis> The thesaurus helps you "
"enhance the quality of your writing and make it more effective by allowing "
"you to find a more appropriate synonym for a selected word."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">同义词提示:</emphasis> 同义词提示功能 "
"使你可以找到更加适合特定上下文环境的措辞"
"从而有效提高作品的语言质量。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:241(para)
msgid ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\"> Autocorrect:</emphasis> Autocorrect is a software "
"function that enables you to reduce your typing effort by automatically "
"correcting common spelling and typing errors. This feature also allows you "
"to automatically apply correct formatting to the text or insert special "
"characters by recognizing particular character usage."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\"> 自动更正:</emphasis> OpenOffice 的自动更正功能"
"可以自动纠正常见的拼写错误和输入错误"
"从而使你的输入工作变得更加轻松。此外，自动更正功能还可以"
"使你自动应用正确的文档格式，并在识别出"
"文字的特殊用法时自动插入特定的特殊字符"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:250(para)
msgid ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">Hyphenation:</emphasis> You can use the "
"hyphenation feature to insert hyphens in words that are too long to fit at "
"the end of a line. It searches the entire document and suggests hyphenation "
"that you can either accept or reject."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">智能断字:</emphasis> 当一个位于句尾的单词"
"长度过大而不得不转入下一行的时候，智能断字功能可以自动在句尾加入连字符号，"
"以保持单词的连贯性。该功能会自动搜索整个文档并做出加入连字符号的建议，"
"你可以自主决定是否需要加入连字符号。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:258(para)
msgid ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">Mail merge:</emphasis> The Mail merge feature "
"allows you to create multiple personalised form letters, labels, envelopes, "
"faxes and e-mail messages by using a form letter template and an address "
"database."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">邮件合并:</emphasis> 邮件合并功能"
"为你提供可供套用的信函模板和地址数据库，使你可以轻松的创建高"
"度定制的信件模板，标签，信封，电报稿"
"和电子邮件。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:217(para)
msgid ""
"OpenOffice.org Writer offers a variety of useful features to help you create "
"basic text documents as well as long and complex or multi-part documents "
"that may include components such as bibliographies, reference tables and "
"indexes. Some of these features are: <placeholder-1/>"
msgstr ""
" OpenOffice 为你提供了大量实用的功能，既可以"
"创建基本的文本文档，也可以胜任拥有"
"参考书目，引文表格和超长索引的格式复杂，章节繁多"
"的文档. 其中一些特性包括: <placeholder-1/>"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:267(title)
msgid "Designing and Structuring"
msgstr "设计和排版"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:272(para)
msgid ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">Style and Formatting window:</emphasis> The Style "
"and Formatting window is one of the common features available in the "
"OpenOffice. org package that can be used consistently in all the "
"applications included in the package. You can use this window to create, "
"assign and modify styles for paragraphs, lists, individual characters, "
"frames and pages."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">“样式和格式”窗口</emphasis> 样式和格式"
"窗口是整个 OpenOffice 办公套件各部分的共同特性，在"
"整个套件所包含的所有程序中都可以使用"
"通过这个窗口，你可以创建，分配和"
"修改段落，表格，框架，页面甚至每一个"
"字的格式。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:282(para)
msgid ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">Navigator:</emphasis> Provides you with an outline "
"view of the entire document and allows you to quickly navigate inside the "
"document. You can also use Navigator to track the objects and elements that "
"are already inserted and to insert new elements into the document."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">导航:</emphasis> 导航功能为你提供"
"整个文档的文档结构图，你可以快速的查看整个文档的结构。"
"你也可以使用导航功能来跟踪已经插入文档中的对象和元素，"
"并使用它来向文档中插入新的元素。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:290(para)
msgid ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">Indexes and Tables:</emphasis> Enable you to "
"insert an index, a table of contents or a bibliography reference in your "
"text document. You can also customise the inserted tables and indexes by "
"defining their structure and appearance."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">索引和表格:</emphasis> 通过"
"这一功能，你可以在文档中插入索引，表格或引文列表。"
"你也可以自行设置插入的表格和索引的"
"结构和外观。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:269(para)
msgid ""
"OpenOffice.org enables you to design and structure your text document by "
"using an assortment of features, including: <placeholder-1/>"
msgstr ""
"OpenOffice 办公套件为你提供了很多实用的特性，"
"使你能够对文档进行设计和排版，这些特性包括 <placeholder-1/>"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:300(title)
msgid "Desktop Publishing"
msgstr "桌面出版"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:306(para)
msgid ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">Text Frames:</emphasis> Acts as a container for "
"text and graphics and can be placed anywhere in a document. You can also use "
"these frames to apply a multi-column layout to your document and render a "
"professional look and style to it."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">图文框:</emphasis> 你可以在图文框"
"中加入文本和图像，并把它们放在文档中的任何位置。你也可以使用"
"框架来对你的文档进行分列，或者设置出其他"
"专业的外观和格式。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:314(para)
msgid ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">Graphics:</emphasis> Allows you to insert a "
"graphic object into your text document from a gallery, a file or any other "
"OpenOffice.org application."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">图形功能:</emphasis> 你可以从"
"任意图片集，文件夹或任何其他 OpenOffice 程序"
"中向你的文档插入图片对象。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:320(para)
msgid ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\"> Tables:</emphasis> OpenOffice.org Writer also "
"enables you to create or insert a table into a text document."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\"> 表格:</emphasis> 使用 OpenOffice，"
"你也可以在文档中创建或插入表格。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:302(para)
msgid ""
"The following features can help you create professionally styled documents, "
"such as brochures, invitations and newsletters: <placeholder-1/>"
msgstr ""
"接下来要讲解的这些特性可以使你创建专业风格的文档，"
"比如宣传册，请柬和新闻稿： <placeholder-1/>"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:328(title)
msgid "Drawing"
msgstr "绘图"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:330(para)
msgid ""
"The drawing functions make it easy for you to create many types of drawings "
"and graphics directly in your text document. You can use the Drawing bar to "
"add various shapes, lines, text and callouts to a current document."
msgstr ""
"绘图功能使你可以很容易地在文档中直接创建多种"
"多样的绘画和图形。你可以使用绘图工具栏来向当前"
"文本中加入各种图形，线条，文本和插图编号。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:337(title)
msgid "Drag and Drop"
msgstr "拖放"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:339(para)
msgid ""
"This unique feature allows you to drag objects from one location to another "
"in the same document, from one OpenOffice document to another and from the "
"Gallery to your OpenOffice document."
msgstr ""
"这一独特的特性使你能够在同一文档中，"
"不同 OpenOffice 程序中拖曳对象，你"
"也可以将图片从照片集中拖入 OpenOffice 文档。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:345(title)
msgid "The Help Function"
msgstr "帮助功能"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:347(para)
msgid "This is a complete reference for your Writer."
msgstr "OpenOffice Writer拥有完整的帮助文档"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:352(title)
msgid "Performing Basic Word-Processing Tasks"
msgstr "完成基本的文字处理工作"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:354(para)
msgid ""
"You can perform a number of word-processing tasks, such as writing, editing, "
"formatting, reviewing and printing documents, using OpenOffice.org Writer. "
"The word processor also allows you to use various templates, apply different "
"styles to your document, control your page layout and insert, edit and "
"create graphics inside your text document. Instructions to perform some of "
"the basic word-processing tasks in Writer are described in the following "
"sections."
msgstr ""
"通过使用 OpenOffice Writer，你可以完成大量文字处理"
"任务。比如撰写，编辑，排版，批阅和打印文档。"
"你也可以在使用大量的模板，在文档中应用各种不同"
"的样式，控制页面布局，插入，编辑和创建图形。"
"在接下来的部分中，我们就将讲授"
"如何使用这一程序来完成一些最基本的"
"文字处理工作。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:363(title)
msgid "Entering and Formatting Text"
msgstr "输入和格式化文本"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:365(para)
msgid ""
"OpenOffice.org Writer is primarily used for writing and formatting text. You "
"can enter text using your keyboard and then apply a variety of formats to "
"the text, as per the document's requirements."
msgstr ""
"首先，OpenOffice Writer 可以用来撰写和编辑文本。你"
"可以使用键盘输入一段文本，然后根据不同的要求来"
"进行各种编辑工作。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:372(title)
msgid ""
"You can use the following steps to enter and format text using "
"OpenOffice.org Writer:"
msgstr ""
"通过以下的步骤，你可以在 OpenOffice Writer 中输入和"
"编辑文本。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:376(para)
msgid ""
"On the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Applications</emphasis> menu, point to "
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">Office</emphasis> and then click <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Openoffice.org Word Processor</emphasis>. A blank text "
"document opens."
msgstr ""
"在<emphasis role=\"strong\">程序</emphasis>菜单中，指向"
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">办公</emphasis>然后单击<emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Openoffice.org 文字处理</emphasis>。就能打开"
"一个空白文档。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:382(title)
msgid "Launching Writer"
msgstr "运行 Writer"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:394(para)
msgid ""
"Depending on what you want to do, you can either create a letter, memo, note "
"or an entire novel from scratch, or you may start with a predefined template "
"or sample that is suitable for your requirements."
msgstr ""
"根据你的不同需要，你可以创建信件，记事，笔记"
"甚至整部小说。你也可以打开一个符合要求的预设模板"
"或示例。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:399(para)
msgid ""
"To access the templates and samples, on the <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">File</emphasis> menu, point to <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">New</emphasis> and then click <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Templates and Documents</emphasis>. Alternatively, you can "
"press SHIFT+CTRL+N. The <emphasis role=\"strong\">Templates and "
"Documents</emphasis> dialogue box opens."
msgstr ""
"如要使用模板和示例，在<emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">文件</emphasis> 菜单中, 指向<emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">新建</emphasis>然后单击<emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">模板和文档</emphasis>。或者你也可以直接"
"按下 SHIFT+CTRL+N。即可打开<emphasis role=\"strong\">模板和"
"文档</emphasis>对话框"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:407(title)
msgid "Accessing Templates and Documents"
msgstr "使用模板和文档"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:419(para)
msgid ""
"You can view the various categories of available templates in the middle "
"column of the Templates and Documents dialogue box. If you want to use a "
"template to create your document, you can double-click a category. This will "
"display the various templates associated with that category. Select a "
"template of your choice and then start working on it."
msgstr ""
"你可以在对话框的中间这栏里浏览各种"
"可用的模板的分类，如果你想要使用一个"
"模板来创建你的文档，你可以双击一个分类来"
"查看分类下的所有模板。挑选一个"
"模板，然后就可以开始你的工作了。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:426(para)
msgid ""
"However, you may also decide to work with the default blank document. To "
"continue working with the blank document, exit the <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Templates and Documents</emphasis> dialogue box by clicking "
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">Close</emphasis> in the top-right corner of the "
"dialogue box."
msgstr ""
"如果你要从默认的空白文档开始工作，"
"那么就点击右上角的<emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">关闭</emphasis>按钮来关掉"
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">模板和文档</emphasis>对话"
"框。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:433(title)
msgid "Accessing Templates"
msgstr "使用模板"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:446(emphasis)
msgid ""
"If students need to know more about using samples and templates, you can "
"tell them how to use various wizards, available under the File menu, to "
"create user-defined templates, such as faxes and letters. These templates "
"can later be used to create further documents."
msgstr ""
"如果有学生想要知道更多使用示例和模板的知识，"
"请指导他们使用文件菜单下的各种向导，来"
"创建自定义模板，比如电报稿和信件。将来这些模板"
"也可以被用来创建其他文档。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:455(para)
msgid ""
"After you have created the document, you can use the various formatting "
"features provided in Writer to change the text display or emphasise specific "
"areas in your document. You can use the following options available on the "
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">Formatting</emphasis> toolbar to perform some of "
"the most common formatting tasks."
msgstr ""
"创建文档完成后，你就可以使用程序提供的"
"各种特性来改变文字显示效果或加粗显示"
"文档中的特定部分。你可以使用<emphasis role=\"strong\">格式</emphasis>菜单"
"中的以下选项来完成一些"
"最常见的格式设置任务。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:463(title)
msgid "The Formatting Toolbar"
msgstr "格式工具栏"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:475(para)
msgid ""
"You can use the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Style and Formatting</emphasis> "
"window to perform a complete document makeover."
msgstr ""
"你可以使用<emphasis role=\"strong\">样式和格式</emphasis> "
"窗口来完成完整的文档格式设置工作。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:479(para)
msgid ""
"To open the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Style and Formatting</emphasis> "
"window, on the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Format</emphasis> menu, click "
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">Style and Formatting</emphasis>. The <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Style and Formatting</emphasis> window appears."
msgstr ""
"要打开<emphasis role=\"strong\">样式和格式</emphasis> "
"窗口，请在<emphasis role=\"strong\">格式</emphasis>菜单下，单击"
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">格式和样式</emphasis>. 就会出现<emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">格式和样式</emphasis>窗口。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:486(title)
msgid "Accessing Style and Formatting Window"
msgstr "使用格式和样式窗口"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:498(para)
msgid ""
"You can use this window to select and modify the existing style or create a "
"new style. Clicking one of the icons below the title bar of the <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Style and Formatting</emphasis> window will display a list "
"of styles in a particular category, such as a list or a paragraph."
msgstr ""
"你可以使用这个窗口来选定和修改已有的样式"
"或者创建新的样式。按下窗口标题栏下方的图标，"
"就会显示各个分类下的样式"
"列表，比如段落样式列表等。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:505(title)
msgid "The Style and Formatting Icons"
msgstr "样式和格式图标"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:517(para)
msgid ""
"By default, when you open the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Style and "
"Formatting</emphasis> window, the <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Paragraph</emphasis><emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Style</emphasis> icon is selected. All the styles listed in "
"this category are displayed in the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Style and "
"Formatting</emphasis> window. You can start restyling individual parts of "
"the current document by selecting specific parts of the document and "
"applying an existing style by double-clicking that style."
msgstr ""
"默认情况下，当你打开<emphasis role=\"strong\">样式和"
"格式</emphasis>窗口时，<emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">段落</emphasis><emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">样式</emphasis>图标处于被选定状态。所有在这一"
"分类下的样式都会被列在<emphasis role=\"strong\">样式和"
"格式</emphasis>窗口中。通过选定文档中的"
"特定部分，然后双击你需要的样式，就"
"可以应用你所需要的样式了。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:528(title)
msgid "Applying a Style"
msgstr "使用样式"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:540(para)
msgid ""
"However, if you want to modify an existing style, you can simply right-click "
"that style and select <emphasis role=\"strong\">Modify.</emphasis> This "
"displays a new pop-up window. You can redefine almost all aspects of the "
"selected style using the various options available under the different tabs."
msgstr ""
"如果你需要修改现存的样式，你可以右键单击"
"这一样式并选择<emphasis role=\"strong\">修改</emphasis>。然后会"
"弹出一个新的窗口，通过使用不同标签下的各种选项，"
"你几乎可以自定义样式的所有方面。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:546(para)
msgid ""
"Modify the specifications of the selected style, and click <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">OK</emphasis> to apply the changes."
msgstr ""
"修改所选定样式的细节，然后单击<emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">确定</emphasis>来应用这些改变。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:550(title)
msgid "Modifying a Style"
msgstr "修改样式"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:562(para)
msgid ""
"Double-click the modified style to reflect the changes in the selected text."
msgstr ""
"双击所修改的样式以查看被选定文本的改变情况。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:566(title)
msgid "Applying the Modified Style"
msgstr "使用修改后的样式"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:578(para)
msgid "You can customize all other parts of the document in the same way."
msgstr "你可以用同样的方法自定义文档的其他任何部分。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:584(para)
msgid ""
"If the students want to know more about the various formatting options "
"available, you can give them the following information:"
msgstr ""
"如果学生们想要知道更多关于格式选项的内容，你"
"可以向他们提供如下信息。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:588(emphasis)
msgid "OpenOffice.org provides several ways to apply styles. These are:"
msgstr "OpenOffice.org 提供了几种方法来应用样式，它们包括："

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:591(emphasis)
msgid "Using the Styles and Formatting window."
msgstr "使用格式和样式窗口。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:596(emphasis)
msgid "Using Fill Format mode."
msgstr "使用格式填充模式。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:601(emphasis)
msgid "Using the Apply Style list on the Formatting bar."
msgstr "使用格式工具栏上的应用格式列表。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:606(emphasis)
msgid "Assigning styles to shortcut keys."
msgstr "为样式分配快捷键"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:611(emphasis)
msgid "Using AutoFormat."
msgstr "使用自动格式"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:616(para)
msgid ""
"In addition, describe the procedure to create a new style and add it to the "
"Style and Formatting window."
msgstr ""
"另外，向他们介绍创建新的样式并把"
"它们加入样式和格式窗口的方法"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:623(title)
msgid "Inserting Tables"
msgstr "插入表格"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:625(para)
msgid ""
"To insert a table in a text document, position the cursor where you want the "
"table to appear and then follow the procedure described below:"
msgstr ""
"要在文档中插入表格，请将鼠标指向你希望"
"插入表格的区域，然后按照以下步骤进行操作："

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:630(para)
msgid ""
"On the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Table</emphasis> menu, point to <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Insert</emphasis> and then click <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Table.</emphasis> The <emphasis role=\"strong\">Insert "
"Table</emphasis> dialogue box opens."
msgstr ""
"在<emphasis role=\"strong\">表格</emphasis>菜单中，指向<emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">插入</emphasis>然后单击<emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">表格</emphasis>，即可打开<emphasis role=\"strong\">插入"
"表格</emphasis>对话框。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:636(emphasis)
msgid "Inserting a Table"
msgstr "插入一张表格"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:649(para)
msgid ""
"You can use the various options present in the dialogue box to specify some "
"of the table properties."
msgstr ""
"你可以使用对话框中的各种选项来设置"
"一些表格属性。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:653(emphasis)
msgid "Specifying Table Properties"
msgstr "设置表格属性"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:667(para)
msgid ""
"To directly insert a table with the default properties, click the Table icon "
"on the Standard toolbar and select the table size in the graphic that "
"appears. To create the table, click the cell that you want to be on the last "
"row of the last column."
msgstr ""
"要使用默认属性直接插入表格，单击工具栏上的"
"表格图标，然后在出现的图形框中选择表格尺寸。"
"要创建表格，单击你所需设置的最后一列"
"最后一行额单元格。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:676(para)
msgid ""
"Specify the table properties and click <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">OK.</emphasis> The table is inserted at the specified "
"location in your text document. By default, Writer creates a table as wide "
"as the page margins, with all the rows having the same height and all the "
"columns having the same width. To adjust the column and rows and customise "
"the table further, right-click the table and select <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Table</emphasis> from the short-cut menu. The <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Table Format</emphasis> dialogue box opens."
msgstr ""
"设置表格属性，然后单击<emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">确定。</emphasis>就可以在文档的特定部分"
"插入表格。默认情况下，程序会创建与页面宽度相同的"
"表格，所有的行有相同的行高，所有的列"
"有相同的列宽。如果需要调整行和列的属性，并进一步"
"设置表格，右键单击表格，在弹出菜单中选择<emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">表格</emphasis>按钮。即可打开<emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">表格格式</emphasis>对话框。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:686(para)
msgid ""
"Now you can use this dialogue box to define finer specifications for the "
"table such as alignment, column width, text flow, borders and background."
msgstr ""
"现在你就可以在这个对话框中设置更多选项，"
"比如对齐方式，列宽，文字方向，边框和背景等等。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:690(para)
msgid ""
"Define the table specifications as per your requirements and preferences, "
"and click <emphasis role=\"strong\">OK</emphasis> to apply the changes."
msgstr ""
"根据你的要求和偏好定义表格细节，然后"
"单击<emphasis role=\"strong\">确定</emphasis>来应用这些改变。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:695(emphasis)
msgid "Customising the Table Format"
msgstr "自定义表格格式"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:708(para)
msgid ""
"The defined specifications are applied to the table. To arrange the data "
"within one of the table cells into another table, you can create nested "
"tables. Writer permits you to create as many layers of nested tables as you "
"want."
msgstr ""
"定义好的表格细节会被应用。如果要将一个单元格"
"中的数据用另一个表格形式来展现，你可以创建"
"嵌套表格。Writer 允许你创建不限数量的嵌套"
"表格。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:713(para)
msgid ""
"To create a nested table, click the cell in which you want the nested table "
"to appear, then follow the procedure for inserting a new table. A nested "
"table appears in the specified cell within the larger table."
msgstr ""
"要创建嵌套表格，单击你需要创建嵌套表格的单元格，"
"然后按照创建新表格的步骤操作一遍。"
"一个嵌套表格就会出现在这个单元格中。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:719(emphasis)
msgid "Creating a Nested Table"
msgstr "创建嵌套表格"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:732(para)
msgid ""
"You can now define the finer specifications of the nested table using the "
"Table Format dialogue box and then populate the table with data."
msgstr ""
"你可以使用表格格式对话框来为"
"嵌套的表格定义更多细节，然后填入数据。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:737(emphasis)
msgid "The Nested Table"
msgstr "嵌套表格"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:750(title)
msgid "Inserting Images"
msgstr "插入图片"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:752(para)
msgid ""
"OpenOffice.org allows you to import images of various file formats, "
"including the most common file types such as JPEG, PNG, BMP and GIF. Images "
"can be inserted from a file, the OpenOffice.org Gallery, a scanner, the "
"Internet, or a graphics programme."
msgstr ""
"OpenOffice.org 办公套件允许你插入各种不同格式的图像，"
"包括最流行的图像格式如 JPEG, PNG, BMP 和 GIF。你可以"
"从文件夹，OpenOffice 图片集，扫描仪，互联"
"网或图像程序中插入图像。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:759(title)
msgid "To insert an image into your text document from a file:"
msgstr "要从文件夹向文档中插入图片："

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:762(para)
msgid ""
"Position the cursor at the location in the document where you want the "
"picture to be inserted. On the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Insert</emphasis> "
"menu, point to <emphasis role=\"strong\">Picture</emphasis> and then click "
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">From File</emphasis>. The <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Insert Picture</emphasis> dialogue box opens."
msgstr ""
"将鼠标放在需要插入图片的地方，"
"在<emphasis role=\"strong\">插入</emphasis> "
"菜单中，指向<emphasis role=\"strong\">图片</emphasis>然后单击"
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">来自文件</emphasis>。即可打开<emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">插入图片</emphasis>对话框。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:771(para)
msgid ""
"To insert the file, navigate to the desired file and select it. You can "
"select the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Preview</emphasis> check box at the "
"bottom of the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Insert Picture</emphasis> dialogue "
"box to preview the selected image in a pane and verify whether you have "
"selected the correct image. Click <emphasis role=\"strong\">Open</emphasis> "
"to insert the image in your document."
msgstr ""
"要插入文件，找到并选定需要插入的文件，你可以"
"选定<emphasis role=\"strong\">插入图片</emphasis>对话框底部"
"的<emphasis role=\"strong\">预览</emphasis>选项"
"来预览这一图片以确定你是否选定了"
"正确的图片。单击<emphasis role=\"strong\">打开</emphasis> "
"来把图片插入文档中。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:780(title)
msgid "Inserting Image"
msgstr "插入图片"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:793(para)
msgid "Explain the following:"
msgstr "解释以下内容"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:795(emphasis)
msgid ""
"Selecting the Link check box creates a link of the selected file inside your "
"text document, instead of saving a copy of the image in your document. As a "
"result, though you'll be able to view the image in the document, when the "
"image is saved, the document will contain only a reference to that image but "
"not the image itself. Linking an image has the following advantages and "
"disadvantages:"
msgstr ""
"选中链接复选框可以在你的文档中"
"创建一个链接，而不是在文档中也保存一份图片。"
"这样做的结果是，尽管你可以在文档中看到图片，当"
"图片被保存以后，这个文档将只包括一个指向该图片的链接而不是"
"图片本身。这种链接图片的方式优缺点"
"如下："

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:803(emphasis)
msgid ""
"It reduces the size of your document when it is saved because the image is "
"not included in it."
msgstr ""
"当保存文档时，文档的尺寸会减小，因为"
"图片本身并没有被包括在文档中。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:809(emphasis)
msgid ""
"You can edit or modify the image separately without making any changes in "
"the document and can view the modified image the next time you open the "
"document."
msgstr ""
"你无须打开文档即可单独修改"
"图片，并且在下次打开文档时可以看到"
"修改后的图片。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:816(emphasis)
msgid ""
"When you wish to send the document to someone, you need to send both the "
"document and the image otherwise, the receiver will not be able to view the "
"linked image."
msgstr ""
"当你要把文档发送给其他人时，你"
"需要同时发送文档和图片，否则，受到文档的人将"
"看不到链接的图片。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:826(para)
msgid ""
"The image is inserted at the specified location in your document. If the "
"image does not fit perfectly into your document, you should resize it."
msgstr ""
"图片会被插入到你文档的特定地点。如果"
"图片的大小没有完全符合你的要求，你可以重设图片大小"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:830(para)
msgid ""
"To resize the image while maintaining its proportions, select the image and "
"then press and hold the SHIFT key. When you select an image, some square "
"points (known as \"handles\") appear along its perimeter. While holding down "
"the SHIFT key, click and drag one of the handles on the image to modify its "
"size."
msgstr ""
"要在保持图片属性的情况下重设其大小，请选定图片，然后"
"按住SHIFT键不动。当你选定一张图片后，一些小方"
"块（被称为“手柄”）会出现在图片的边缘。在按住Shift键"
"的同时按下并拖曳这些手柄来调整图片的"
"大小。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:837(title)
msgid "Resizing the Inserted Image"
msgstr "重设插入图片的大小"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:850(para)
msgid ""
"Explain the difference between a scaled and an unscaled resize, and "
"emphasise the advantages of the scaled resize performed above."
msgstr ""
"请向学生解释按比例调整和不按比例调整之间的区别，"
"并强调上面这种按比例调整方式的优越性。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:857(para)
msgid ""
"After you have resized the image, you need to position the image "
"appropriately in the document. You can arrange and align images using the "
"tools on the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Frame toolbar</emphasis>, which "
"appears below the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Standard toolbar</emphasis> when "
"you select a graphic for the first time."
msgstr ""
"在重设完图片的尺寸后，你需要将图片防盗"
"文档中的合适位置。要调整和对其图片，可以"
"使用<emphasis role=\"strong\">框架工具栏</emphasis>中的工具。这个工具栏会在"
"你首次选中一幅图片的时候出现在<emphasis role=\"strong\">标准工具栏</emphasis>的"
"下方。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:864(para)
msgid ""
"Alternatively, you can right-click the image and then select from the "
"available options, such as <emphasis role=\"strong\">Arrange, "
"Wrap</emphasis> or <emphasis role=\"strong\">Anchor,</emphasis> on the short-"
"cut menu."
msgstr ""
"另一种办法是，你可以右键单击图片，然后在快捷菜单中选择例如"
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">排序，"
"对齐</emphasis>或者<emphasis role=\"strong\">锁定</emphasis>等"
"选项。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:870(title)
msgid "Positioning the Inserted Image"
msgstr "放置插入的图片"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:882(para)
msgid ""
"After you have selected appropriate positioning options for the image, you "
"may obtain a result similar to the following screenshot."
msgstr ""
"在选定了合适的图片选项后，你也许会"
"看到类似于下面这张截图的情形。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:887(title)
msgid "The Inserted Image"
msgstr "插入的图片"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:900(title)
msgid "Printing Documents"
msgstr "打印文档"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:903(para)
msgid ""
"On the <emphasis role=\"strong\">File</emphasis> menu, click <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Print</emphasis>. The <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Print</emphasis> dialogue box opens. You can use this "
"dialogue box to specify the printer to be used (in case you have more than "
"one printer installed on your system), the pages to be printed, and the "
"number of copies to be printed. You can also click the <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Properties</emphasis> button in the <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Print</emphasis> dialogue box to define the properties of "
"the printer, such as orientation, the paper tray to be used and the paper "
"size to be printed."
msgstr ""
"在<emphasis role=\"strong\">文件</emphasis>菜单下，单击<emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">打印</emphasis>。就会弹出<emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">打印</emphasis>对话框。你可以使用这个"
"对话框来选定要使用的打印机（如果你有不止一台"
"打印机的话），需要打印的页码，以及"
"需要打印的份数。你也可以单击<emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">打印</emphasis>对话框中的<emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">属性</emphasis>按钮来设置打印机的属性，比"
"如说方向，需要使用的纸盒和需要打印的纸张"
"大小。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:914(para)
msgid ""
"To define printer options for the current document, click the <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Options</emphasis> button in the <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Print</emphasis> dialogue box."
msgstr ""
"要为当前文档设置打印属性，单击<emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">打印</emphasis>对话框中的<emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">选项</emphasis>按钮。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:919(emphasis)
msgid "Printing a Document"
msgstr "打印一份文档"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:932(para)
msgid ""
"The <emphasis role=\"strong\">Printer Options</emphasis> dialogue box "
"enables you to select specific sections from the current document for "
"printing. For example, to save toner or ink, you may not want to print the "
"background and the graphics in the document. You can specify these details "
"under the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Content</emphasis> section by selecting "
"or clearing the appropriate check boxes."
msgstr ""
"通过使用<emphasis role=\"strong\">打印选项</emphasis>对话框，"
"你可以选择当前文档中的特定部分来进行打印。例"
"如为了节省墨粉或墨水，你也许不希望印出文档的"
"背景和图像，你可以通过控"
"制<emphasis role=\"strong\">内容</emphasis>中的复选框来"
"确定这些细节。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:940(para)
msgid ""
"Similarly, you can define the required printing options in the <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Pages</emphasis> and <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Notes</emphasis> section. After specifying the details, "
"click <emphasis role=\"strong\">OK</emphasis> to save your settings."
msgstr ""
"类似的，你也可以在<emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">页面</emphasis>和<emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">批注</emphasis>中设定所需的打印细节。设定完这些细节后，"
"单击<emphasis role=\"strong\">确定</emphasis>来保存这些设置。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:947(emphasis)
msgid "Defining Printer Options"
msgstr "设定打印选项"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:960(para)
msgid ""
"You can now start printing the document by clicking <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">OK</emphasis> on the <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Print</emphasis> dialogue box."
msgstr ""
"现在你可以单击<emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">打印</emphasis>对话框中的<emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">确定</emphasis>按钮来开始打印文档了。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:967(para)
msgid ""
"Making changes in the Printer Options dialogue box will only apply to the "
"current document and not change your default settings permanently."
msgstr ""
"在打印选项对话框中作出的修改会只应用于"
"当前的文档，而不会永久改变你的默认打印设置。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:975(emphasis)
msgid ""
"If the students want to know about the procedure to select the default print "
"options, provide them the following information:"
msgstr ""
"如果学生们想要了解选择默认打印机的方式，请"
"向他们提供以下信息："

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:979(emphasis)
msgid ""
"To select the default print options, On the Tools menu, click Options."
msgstr ""
"要选择默认打印机，在工具菜单中单击选项"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:982(emphasis)
msgid "The OpenOffice.org - Print dialogue box opens."
msgstr "The OpenOffice.org - 打印对话框打开时的状态。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:987(emphasis)
msgid ""
"In the left navigation panel, expand OpenOffice.org Writer and then select "
"Print."
msgstr ""
"在左侧面板中，展开 OpenOffice.org Writer 然后选择"
"打印。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:993(emphasis)
msgid ""
"Select the required options and click OK to apply the changes to the default "
"print settings."
msgstr ""
"设定所需的选项，然后按下确定来将这些改变应用到默认的"
"打印设置中。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1003(title)
msgid "Saving Documents"
msgstr "保存文档"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1005(para)
msgid ""
"You can save your Writer document in the same way as you save any other "
"document. To save a new text document:"
msgstr ""
"保存 Writer 文档的方法和保存其他类型文档的方法是一样的。"
"要保存一个新的文档："

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1009(para)
msgid ""
"On the <emphasis role=\"strong\">File</emphasis> menu, click <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Save As</emphasis>. The <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Save</emphasis> dialogue box opens."
msgstr ""
"在<emphasis role=\"strong\">文件</emphasis>菜单中，单击<emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">保存</emphasis>。打开<emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">保存</emphasis>对话框。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1014(emphasis)
msgid "Saving the Document"
msgstr "保存文档"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1027(para)
msgid ""
"Navigate to the directory where you want to save the file, enter the file "
"name and click <emphasis role=\"strong\">Save</emphasis> to save the file at "
"the desired location."
msgstr ""
"找到你想要保存文档的路径，输入"
"文件名，按下<emphasis role=\"strong\">保存</emphasis>来将文档保存在"
"你需要的位置。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1032(para)
msgid ""
"OpenOffice.org also allows you to save your document in a number of other "
"file formats, including Microsoft Word, Rich Text, Star Writer and as an "
"HTML document. This enables you to share your documents with other people "
"who use other office applications, such as Office."
msgstr ""
"OpenOffice.org 也允许你将文档保存为其他的"
"格式，包括 Microsoft Word， Rich Text，Star Writer 和"
"HTML 文件。使你可以和使用其他办公软件（比如 Office）的人"
"共享文件。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1038(para)
msgid ""
"If you would like to save your current document as a Word file, select the "
"appropriate type of Word format from the drop-down menu at the bottom of the "
"dialogue box. Then, click <emphasis role=\"strong\">Save</emphasis> to save "
"the file as a Word document."
msgstr ""
"如果你想要把当前文件保存为 Word 文档，选择"
"在对话框下部的下拉菜单中选择合适的 Word 版本，"
"然后按下<emphasis role=\"strong\">保存</emphasis>来将这一文件"
"保存为 Word 文档。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1045(emphasis)
msgid "Saving in Word Format"
msgstr "保存为 Word 格式"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1061(title)
msgid "Using OpenOffice.org Calc"
msgstr "使用 OpenOffice.org Calc"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1063(para)
msgid ""
"Calc is the spreadsheet component of the OpenOffice.org office software "
"suite. The comprehensive range of advanced functions included in Calc helps "
"professionals accomplish complex tasks. At the same time, Calc is user-"
"friendly, which makes it easier for new users. This topic will familiarise "
"you with its key features and teach you how to perform some basic "
"spreadsheet functions."
msgstr ""
"Calc 是 OpenOffice.org 系列办公套件中的表格制作 "
"工具。该软件具有一系列先进的功能，使专业人员"
"能够完成复杂的表格制作任务。同时，它对用户也"
"十分友好，即使是新手也能轻易使用。本教程将使你"
"熟悉 Calc 的基本功能，并指导尼如何完成基本的表格"
"制作任务。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1070(para)
msgid ""
"Similar to all other applications in the OpenOffice.org suite, Calc allows "
"you to save spreadsheets in OASIS OpenDocument (ODF) format. This XML-based "
"format enables you to access your spreadsheets from any OpenDocument-"
"compliant software. In addition, Calc allows you to save spreadsheets "
"directly as Portable Document Format (PDF) files without using any "
"additional software."
msgstr ""
"与 OpenOffice.org 办公套件中的其他应用程序相似，Calc 使你"
"能够以开源的 ODF 格式保存数据表格。这一格式基于 XML，使你制作的表格可以在"
"在任何遵循开源文件格式的软件中打开。此外，在 Calc 中你还可以在不借助任何其他软件的情况下把表格直接保存为 PDF 格式。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1078(title)
msgid "Key Features of OpenOffice.org Calc"
msgstr "OpenOffice.org Calc 的主要功能"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1086(title)
msgid "Calculation:"
msgstr "计算"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1088(para)
msgid ""
"OpenOffice.org Calc provides you with over 300 functions for financial, "
"logical, statistical, mathematical and banking operations. This enables you "
"to create formulae to perform complex calculations on your data. In "
"addition, Calc provides you with Function wizard that guides you "
"interactively through the creation of formulae."
msgstr ""
"OpenOffice.org Calc 为你提供了超过三百种财政，逻辑，统计，数学和银行操作方面的计算函数，使你可以"
"为你的复杂数据计算创建自定义表达式。此外，Calc 程序还提供交互性的函数创建向导来帮助你建立自定义表达式。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1096(para)
msgid ""
"Another feature of OpenOffice.org Calc is that it allows you to create "
"natural language formulae using words such as sales - costs."
msgstr ""
"OpenOffice.org Calc 的另一项重要功能是使你能够使用自然语言创建表达式，例如“销售额-成本”。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1103(title)
msgid "Scenario Manager:"
msgstr "方案管理器"


#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1105(para)
msgid ""
"Allows you to perform 'what-if' analyses and view the result of changes made "
"to any factor of the calculation. For example, when performing a loan "
"calculation, you can change the period of the loan and can view the "
"resulting calculations for the loan-repayment amount or the interest rate."
msgstr ""
"通过使用方案管理器，你可以对计算过程进行可能性分析并查看对计算过程作出的任何改变及其可能结果。"
"例如，当你进行一次贷款计算时，你可以在改变贷款时间数据的同时查看到相应的还贷金额和利率。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1115(title)
msgid "Data Pilot:"
msgstr "数据透视表"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1117(para)
msgid ""
"Enables you to compare, combine and arrange large amounts of data. It helps "
"you pull in raw data from corporate databases, cross-tabulate, summarise and "
"convert the data into meaningful information. You can use Data Pilot to "
"create interactive tables, which allows the data to be frequently arranged, "
"rearranged or summarised according to different points of view."
msgstr ""
"你可以通过数据透视表来对大量的数据进行比较，结合和排列。"
"你可以从企业数据库中提取原始数据，交叉制表，进行总结，把这些数据变成有用的信息。"
"你可以使用数据透视表来创建具有交互性的表格，根据不同的观点频繁地排列，重排和总结数据。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1129(title)
msgid "Dynamic Charts:"
msgstr "动态表格"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1131(para)
msgid ""
"As the name suggests, these charts update automatically as the data in the "
"spreadsheet changes."
msgstr ""
"顾名思义，动态表格可以根据表中数据的变化进行自动更新。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1138(title)
msgid "Opening and Saving Microsoft Files:"
msgstr "打开和保存 Microsoft Office 专用格式的文件。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1140(para)
msgid ""
"Calc allows you to use your old Microsoft spreadsheets and save your work in "
"Microsoft Excel or a variety of other formats. This facilitates the easy "
"sharing of data with others using Microsoft or similar applications."
msgstr ""
"微软专有格式的数据表格也可以在 Calc 中打开，你可以把你的表格保存为 Excel 等其他格式。Calc 的这一功能"
"使你可以很方便的与使用 Microsoft Office 办公套件或其他类似程序的同事共享数据。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1080(para)
msgid ""
"Calc is a fully featured office application that includes all the advanced "
"analysis, charting and decision-making features that you expect from a high-"
"end spreadsheet. Some of the key features of OpenOffice.org Calc are: "
"<placeholder-1/>"
msgstr ""
"Calc 是一个功能完善的办公软件，涵盖了一个高端制表软件所应有的一切分析，制表和决策方面特性。"
"其中一些重要特性包括："
"<placeholder-1/>"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1150(title)
msgid "Performing Basic Spreadsheet Tasks"
msgstr "完成基本的制表任务"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1152(para)
msgid ""
"Similar to any other spreadsheet application, Calc is used to process "
"numerical information or text in tabular form. It is primarily used for "
"tabulating numerical figures. It also allows you to sort and manipulate "
"data, apply arithmetic, mathematic and statistical functions to data sets "
"and represent the datasets in charts or graphical forms. The following "
"sections describe the instructions to perform some basic spreadsheet tasks "
"in Calc."
msgstr ""
"与其他任何制表程序类似，Calc 可以用于处理制表过程中所遇到的大量信息和文本。"
"你可以用它将大量的数据制成表格，也可以对数据进行分类管理，应用算术，数学和统计学"
"函数来处理数据集，并将数据集用表格或图表展示出来。"
"在接下来的部分中，我们将介绍如何使用 Calc 来完成一些基本的数据表格处理任务。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1161(title)
msgid "Formatting Tables and Cells"
msgstr "设计表格和单元格"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1163(para)
msgid "To format tables and cells in a Calc spreadsheet:"
msgstr "要在 Calc 中对表格和单元格进行设计："

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1166(para)
msgid ""
"On the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Applications</emphasis> menu, point to "
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">Office</emphasis> and then click <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">OpenOffice.org Spreadsheet</emphasis> to open a Calc "
"spreadsheet. A new Calc window opens."
msgstr ""
"在<emphasis role=\"strong\">应用程序</emphasis>菜单中，指向"
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">办公</emphasis>然后按下<emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">OpenOffice.org 电子表格</emphasis>，即可"
"在新窗口中打开一个电子表格。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1172(emphasis)
msgid "Launching Calc"
msgstr "打开 Calc"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1184(para)
msgid ""
"Some of the key components of the main Calc window are described below:"
msgstr "下面介绍一下 Calc 主窗口的一些关键部件："

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1188(emphasis)
msgid "The Calc Window"
msgstr "Calc 主窗口"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1200(para)
msgid ""
"The Name box contains the cell and the row number, called the cell "
"reference, of the current or active cell."
msgstr ""
"名称框包含了单元格的列号和行号，可以快速查看当前或活动单元格的位置。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1205(para)
msgid "The active cell indicates the selected cell currently in use."
msgstr "活动单元格，指的是当前被选定并正在使用的单元格。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1210(para)
msgid "The Function wizard opens the Function Wizard dialogue box."
msgstr "函数向导按钮，可以打开函数向导对话框。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1215(para)
msgid ""
"The Sum button allows you to calculate the sum of the numbers in the cells "
"that are above the current cell."
msgstr ""
"求和按钮，用来计算当前单元格以上的所有单元格中数据的总和。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1220(para)
msgid ""
"Clicking the Function button inserts an equals sign into the current cell as "
"well as in the input line, making it ready to accept a formula."
msgstr ""
"按下函数，就可以在当前单元格和输入行中插入一个等号，便于接下来的表达式计算。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1226(para)
msgid ""
"The sheet tabs at the bottom of the sheet indicate the number of worksheets "
"present in the current spreadsheet. By default, a new spreadsheet includes "
"three worksheets."
msgstr ""
"窗口最下方是工作表按钮，显示当前电子表格中的工作表数量，默认情况下一个新的电子表格包括3个工作表。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1234(para)
msgid ""
"After you have entered the required data in the spreadsheet, you can apply "
"different formatting styles to it by selecting from the wide range of "
"options available in Calc. To apply desired formatting to a selected range "
"of cells, on the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Format</emphasis> menu, click "
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">Cells.</emphasis> The <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Format Cells</emphasis> dialogue box opens."
msgstr ""
"在表格中输入所需要的数据以后，你可以利用 Calc 提供的大量选项来对数据应用各种不同的格式。"
"要对选定的单元格应用所需要的格式，在"
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">格式</emphasis>菜单中，单击"
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">单元格</emphasis>，即可打开<emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">单元格格式</emphasis>对话框。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1243(emphasis)
msgid "Formatting Cells"
msgstr "设定单元格格式"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1255(para)
msgid ""
"You can use the various options available under the <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Font, Font Effects</emphasis> and <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Alignment</emphasis> tabs to specify various formatting "
"attributes for the selected text. Similarly, for assigning formatting "
"attributes to numbers, you can select from a number of pre-defined formats "
"available on the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Numbers</emphasis> tab page or "
"define a new one based on your preferences."
msgstr ""
"你可以使用<emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">字体，字体效果</emphasis>和<emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">对齐</emphasis>标签页中的大量选项来对选定的文本"
"设定各种格式属性。类似的，如果要设定数字的格式属性，你可以从"
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">数字</emphasis>数字标签页上的大量预设格式中选择，也"
"可以根据自己的偏好设定一种新的格式。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1264(para)
msgid ""
"The <emphasis role=\"strong\">Format Cells</emphasis> dialogue box also "
"provides you with options to add smart borders and vibrant backgrounds to "
"your spreadsheet. It also allows you to select a background colour, from a "
"spectrum of colours, for your otherwise bland and dull spreadsheet."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">单元格格式</emphasis>对话框同时为你提供了设定数据表"
"边框和背景的选项。如果觉得表格看上去单调无趣，你就可以从光谱图中选择一种背景色。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1270(para)
msgid ""
"Define the specifications and click <emphasis role=\"strong\">OK</emphasis> "
"to apply the formatting effects."
msgstr ""
"更改相应的选项，然后按下<emphasis role=\"strong\">确定</emphasis>按钮。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1274(emphasis)
msgid "Defining Formatting Attributes"
msgstr "定义格式属性"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1287(para)
msgid ""
"After you have selected formatting attributes for the selected cell range, "
"you may get a result similar to this one."
msgstr ""
"为选定单元格设置属性完毕后，结果大致如图所示。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1291(emphasis)
msgid "The Formatted Spreadsheet"
msgstr "格式设定完毕后的电子表格"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1304(para)
msgid ""
"Calc provides you with another useful feature, called <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Autoformat,</emphasis> which enables you to create "
"attractive and professional table designs without undergoing the time-"
"consuming process of selecting cell groups and assigning different formats "
"to them. The Autoformat feature allows you to quickly apply preset formats "
"to an entire sheet or a selected cell range. To apply Autoformat to a sheet "
"or selected cell range, on the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Format</emphasis> "
"menu, click <emphasis role=\"strong\">Autoformat</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"Calc 的另一个实用的特性被称为<emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">自动格式，</emphasis>使你能够轻松做出极富吸引力的专业级表格，而"
"不用浪费大量时间来选定单元格和设置各种格式属性。"
"自动格式特性使你能够快速地将当前的格式套用到"
"整张表格或选定的单元格区域。要使用自动格式功能，请 "
"在<emphasis role=\"strong\">格式</emphasis> "
"菜单下单击<emphasis role=\"strong\">自动格式</emphasis>。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1315(emphasis)
msgid "Using Autoformat"
msgstr "使用自动格式"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1327(para)
msgid ""
"This displays the AutoFormat dialogue box. To assign a pre-set format to the "
"selected cells, select one from the <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Format</emphasis> list and then click <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">OK</emphasis> to apply the selected format to the selection."
msgstr ""
"将会出现自动格式对话框，要对选定的单元格使用预设的格式，在<emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">格式</emphasis>菜单下选择一个，然后单击<emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">确定</emphasis>来加以应用。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1334(emphasis)
msgid "Selecting a Format"
msgstr "选择一种格式"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1347(para)
msgid ""
"The format of your choice is immediately applied to the selection, and you "
"get an attractive and fully formatted table with very little effort."
msgstr ""
"你所选择的格式会立刻应用到选定区域，你可以不费吹灰之力创造出格式完整，界面美观的表格。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1352(emphasis)
msgid "The Formatted Table"
msgstr "格式化后的表格"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1366(title)
msgid "Entering Values and Formulas"
msgstr "输入数值和表达式"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1368(para)
msgid ""
"A formula is a spreadsheet function, complete with arguments, entered in a "
"cell. All formulae begin with an equal sign and may contain number, text "
"and, in some cases, other data such as format details. The formulae may also "
"contain arithmetic operators, logic operators or function starts."
msgstr ""
"表达式是一种表格中函数，需要与参数一起输入到单元格中。所有的表达式都以一个等号开始，并"
"包含有数字，文本以及其他一些类型的数据。表达式也会含有算术运算符，逻辑运算符以及函数头。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1378(para)
msgid "This table lists some examples of OpenOffice.org formulae:"
msgstr "本表格列出了一些 OpenOffice.org 所使用的表达式示例。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1383(title)
msgid "Calc Formulae"
msgstr "Calc 常用表达式"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1392(emphasis)
msgid "Formulae"
msgstr "表达式"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1395(emphasis)
msgid "Description"
msgstr "简介"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1400(emphasis)
msgid "=SUM(A1:A11)"
msgstr "=SUM(A1:A11)"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1403(para)
msgid "Calculates the sum of the cells A1:A11"
msgstr "计算从 A1 到 A11 单元格的数据总和"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1408(emphasis)
msgid "=EFFECTIVE(5%;12)"
msgstr "=EFFECTIVE(5%;12)"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1411(para)
msgid ""
"Calculates the effective interest for 5% annual nominal interest with 12 "
"payments a year"
msgstr ""
"计算年名义利率为5%且按月支付情况下的有效利率。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1416(emphasis)
msgid "=B1*B2"
msgstr "=B1*B2"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1419(para)
msgid "Displays the result of the multiplication of B1 and B2"
msgstr "显示 B1 和 B2 单元格数值的积"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1424(emphasis)
msgid "=C4-SUM(C10:C14)"
msgstr "=C4-SUM(C10:C14)"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1427(para)
msgid "Calculates C4 minus the sum of cells C10 to C14"
msgstr "计算 C4 单元格数据与 C10 到 C14 单元格数据之和的差"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1434(para)
msgid ""
"The quickest way to enter a formula is to type the formula either in the "
"cell where you want the result to display or in the Input Line on the "
"Formula bar. You can also use the Function wizard, which helps you "
"interactively create formulae."
msgstr ""
"输入表达式最快捷的方式是在单元格中或输入行中键入表达式。你也可以"
"使用函数创建向导来交互式地创建表达式。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1440(title)
msgid "To enter a formula using the Function wizard:"
msgstr "使用函数向导创建表达式："

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1443(para)
msgid ""
"In your spreadsheet, select the cell where you want the formula to be "
"inserted. To allow the Function wizard to guide you through the creation and "
"application of a formula, on the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Formula "
"bar</emphasis>, click <emphasis role=\"strong\">Function Wizard</emphasis>. "
"This opens the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Function Wizard</emphasis> dialogue "
"box."
msgstr ""
"在表格中选定需要插入表达式的位置，"
"要使用函数向导来创建和应用表达式，在<emphasis role=\"strong\">表达式"
"栏</emphasis>，单击<emphasis role=\"strong\">函数向导</emphasis>。"
"即可打开<emphasis role=\"strong\">函数向导</emphasis>对话框。"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1451(title)
msgid "Launching Function Wizard"
msgstr "运行函数向导"

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1463(para)
msgid ""
"You can see the entire range of functions listed in the <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Functions</emphasis> list box. You can also select one "
"category from the Category drop-down list to display the functions listed "
"under that category. Find the desired function from the <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Functions</emphasis> list, and click to select it. You "
"notice that the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Function Wizard</emphasis> "
"dialogue box provides you some information about the selected function to "
"guide you through your selection. After selecting the function, click "
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">Next</emphasis> to proceed with the task of "
"entering a formula."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1476(title)
msgid "Selecting a Function"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1488(para)
msgid ""
"Now, you need to specify the numbers to which you want to apply the formula. "
"To select the numbers, you need to go back to the worksheet."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1492(para)
msgid ""
"Click the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Shrink</emphasis> button to shrink this "
"dialogue box and return to the worksheet."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1496(title)
msgid "Shrinking the Function Wizard Dialogue Box"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1508(para)
msgid ""
"The <emphasis role=\"strong\">Function Wizard</emphasis> dialogue box "
"shrinks to allow you to view the worksheet. To select the cell range, hold "
"down the <emphasis role=\"strong\">SHIFT</emphasis> key and use the mouse to "
"select the cell range containing the desired numbers."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1514(para)
msgid ""
"After selecting the cells, you can go back to the Function wizard by "
"clicking the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Maximize</emphasis> button."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1519(title)
msgid "Selecting the Cell Range"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1531(para)
msgid ""
"The cell reference for the selected cell range automatically appears in the "
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">number 1</emphasis> box and the applied formula, "
"complete with arguments, appears in the <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Formula</emphasis> box at the bottom of the dialogue box. To "
"complete the task of entering a formula, click <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">OK</emphasis>."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1539(title)
msgid "Applying the Formula"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1551(para)
msgid "The solution appears in the cell where you had applied the formula."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1555(title)
msgid "Final Output"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1568(title)
msgid "Inserting Charts"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1570(para)
msgid ""
"You can present your data in the form of charts or graphs to compare your "
"data series visually and view trends in the data. Calc offers you a number "
"of ways to represent spreadsheet data graphically."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1577(title)
msgid "To insert a chart in your spreadsheet:"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1580(para)
msgid ""
"Open a spreadsheet containing data and row and column headings, and select "
"the data to be included in the chart. Then, on the <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Insert</emphasis> menu, select <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Chart</emphasis>. The <emphasis role=\"strong\">Chart "
"Wizard</emphasis> dialogue box appears."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1587(title)
msgid "Launching the Chart Wizard"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1600(para)
msgid ""
"Advise students about the alternate way to insert a chart using the Insert "
"Chart icon from the Standard toolbar."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1606(para)
msgid ""
"On the first page of the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Chart wizard</emphasis>, "
"you can select the chart type and preview the chart output. Calc allows you "
"to select from a wide range of 2D and 3D charts. You may decide to follow "
"the rest of the instructions of the Chart Wizard by clicking <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Next</emphasis> or you can click <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Finish</emphasis> to insert a chart in your document."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1615(title)
msgid "Selecting the Chart Type"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1627(para)
msgid ""
"The chart is inserted at the specified location in your spreadsheet. You can "
"now move and resize the chart and edit it further to suit your requirements."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1632(title)
msgid "The Inserted Chart"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1645(title)
msgid "Exporting Spreadsheets to PDF"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1647(para)
msgid ""
"Like the other OpenOffice.org applications, you can export your spreadsheets "
"from Calc as PDF files. With OpenOffice.org you do not need any additional "
"third party software to convert your documents into PDF format."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1654(title)
msgid "To export your spreadsheet as a PDF:"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1657(para)
msgid ""
"On the <emphasis role=\"strong\">File</emphasis> menu, click <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Export as PDF</emphasis>. The <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Export</emphasis> dialogue box appears."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1662(title)
msgid "Exporting Spreadsheet as PDF"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1674(para)
msgid ""
"The four tabbed pages in this dialogue box allow you to define options, such "
"as the pages to be included in the PDF, the type of compression to be used "
"and the level of security to be assigned to the file. After defining these "
"specifications, click <emphasis role=\"strong\">Export</emphasis> to "
"continue."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1681(title)
msgid "Defining PDF Options"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1693(para)
msgid ""
"Provide a file name for your spreadsheet and navigate to the directory where "
"you want to save it. Click <emphasis role=\"strong\">Save</emphasis> to "
"export the spreadsheet as a PDF file."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1699(title)
msgid "Saving as PDF"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1712(para)
msgid ""
"To discover an Easter Egg tucked away in Calc, click within any of the cells "
"of your spreadsheet, type <emphasis role=\"strong\">= "
"GAME(\"StarWars\")</emphasis> and start playing right away."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1720(para)
msgid "Your spreadsheet is now displayed as a PDF file."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1723(title)
msgid "The PDF file"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1738(title)
msgid "Using OpenOffice.org Impress"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1740(para)
msgid ""
"Impress is a fully featured presentation tool of the OpenOffice.org office "
"software suite. It enables you to create effective multimedia presentations "
"by creating 2D and 3D clip art and images. It also allows you to create "
"special effects and animations by using high-impact drawing tools."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1746(para)
msgid ""
"OpenOffice.org Impress is similar to Microsoft PowerPoint in its "
"functionality. In addition to making it easy for you to create PDF files "
"from presentations, Impress lets you export the presentations into ShockWave "
"Flash (SWF) files. This enables you to run the output on any computer that "
"has a Flash player installed."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1753(title)
msgid "Key Features of OpenOffice.org Impress"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1755(para)
msgid "Some of the many useful features of Impress are:"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1758(title)
msgid "Creating Vector Graphics:"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1760(para)
msgid ""
"Impress comes bundled with various drawing tools that allow you to create "
"vector graphics from within the application. You can also export vector "
"graphics to bitmap pictures and, inversely, convert bitmap pictures into "
"vector graphics."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1767(title)
msgid "Creating Slides:"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1769(para)
msgid ""
"Choose from ready-to-use templates or use the drawing and diagram tools to "
"jazz up your slides. Master view adds the elements that you want to appear "
"on all slides of your presentation."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1774(para)
msgid ""
"Further, Impress users have the option to install the Open ClipArt library, "
"which contains a huge selection of images for free use."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1777(para)
msgid ""
"Animations and effects help add spice to your presentations. You can render "
"stunning 2D and 3D effects to your text using Fontwork, which lets you "
"create life-like 3D images easily."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1782(title)
msgid "Publishing Presentations:"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1784(para)
msgid ""
"Impress allows you to publish presentations as handouts, export them into "
"PDF files, convert them into SWF files and publish them as HTML documents. "
"This enables you to access your presentation from a variety of platforms."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1791(title)
msgid "Saving Presentation in Other Formats:"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1793(para)
msgid ""
"Similar to other OpenOffice.Org applications, Impress saves your work in the "
"international OpenDocument format. It also allows you to save your work in "
"other formats such as PowerPoint."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1800(title)
msgid "Creating Multi-Media Presentations"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1803(title)
msgid "Creating, Viewing and Printing a Presentation"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1805(para)
msgid "To create and view presentations using OpenOffice.org Impress:"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1809(para) chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:4465(para)
msgid ""
"On the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Applications</emphasis> menu, point to "
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">Office</emphasis> and then click <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">OpenOffice.org Presentation</emphasis>."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1815(emphasis)
msgid "Launching Impress"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1828(para)
msgid ""
"The <emphasis role=\"strong\">Presentation Wizard</emphasis> dialogue box "
"appears. The <emphasis role=\"strong\">Presentation wizard</emphasis> allows "
"you to define the basic structure of a presentation in three brief steps. "
"You can either continue defining the specifications as guided by the "
"Presentation Wizard or immediately create a new blank presentation by "
"clicking <emphasis role=\"strong\">Create</emphasis>."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1837(emphasis)
msgid "Using the Presentation Wizard"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1851(para)
msgid ""
"To be able to preview the slide template, slide design and slide transition "
"effects, leave the Preview check box selected."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1858(para)
msgid ""
"This figure shows the main Impress window with an empty presentation. From "
"the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Task</emphasis> pane on the left, you can "
"select a layout for your current slide."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1863(emphasis)
msgid "The Impress Window"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1876(para)
msgid ""
"Enter the required text in the provided text boxes to create the first "
"slide. To make your presentation more attractive and professional looking, "
"you can either change the background and format the font size and colour for "
"each slide or simply select a pre-defined template from the <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Master Pages</emphasis> panel."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1883(para)
msgid ""
"Click <emphasis role=\"strong\">Master Pages</emphasis> to open the "
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">Master Pages</emphasis> panel."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1887(emphasis)
msgid "Opening the Master Pages Panel"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1900(para)
msgid ""
"A number of templates are available on the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Master "
"Pages</emphasis> panel. Select the template of your choice to apply a whole "
"new look to your presentation. You can enhance the look of the presentation "
"further by adding various elements, such as objects, pictures and animated "
"images, from the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Insert</emphasis> menu. "
"Alternatively, you can start adding new slides to the presentation."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1908(para)
msgid ""
"You can add a new slide by clicking the <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Slide</emphasis> button on the <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Standard toolbar</emphasis>. Alternatively, click <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Slide</emphasis> on the <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Insert</emphasis> menu."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1915(emphasis)
msgid "Selecting a Slide Template"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1928(para)
msgid ""
"The inserted slide is also formatted as the first slide because that is the "
"layout you selected last. According to the requirements of your "
"presentation, you can select a new format from the <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Layout</emphasis> pane. The new layout has two columns, one "
"for text and the other for images. This allows you to display text along "
"with an associated image on the same slide. Enter the textual content in the "
"provided text boxes, then double-click the house icon to insert a graphic in "
"the provided placeholder."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1939(emphasis)
msgid "Selecting a Slide Layout"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1952(para)
msgid ""
"In the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Insert Picture</emphasis> dialogue box, "
"select the desired image and click <emphasis role=\"strong\">Open</emphasis> "
"to insert it into your slide."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1957(emphasis)
msgid "Inserting Picture in a Slide"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1970(para)
msgid ""
"Notice that the inserted picture is automatically resized to fit into the "
"provided space. You can also insert an image by selecting <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Picture</emphasis> from the <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Insert</emphasis> menu. A picture inserted in this way is "
"not automatically resized, but you can move and resize it as needed. You can "
"insert new slides in a similar fashion."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1978(para)
msgid ""
"Now, you are ready to display your presentation as a slide show. To "
"configure the basic slide show setting, select <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Slide Show Settings</emphasis> from the <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Slide Show</emphasis> menu."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1984(emphasis)
msgid "Setting up a Slide Show"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:1997(para)
msgid ""
"The <emphasis role=\"strong\">Slide Show</emphasis> dialogue box helps you "
"define the basic settings for your slide show. In the <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Range</emphasis> section, you can specify the slides to be "
"included in the presentation and their order of display. In the <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Type</emphasis> section, you can define how to display the "
"slides. Similarly, the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Options</emphasis> section "
"allows you to define various other settings for your presentation."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2006(para)
msgid ""
"After selecting the desired options, click <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">OK</emphasis> to apply the settings."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2010(emphasis)
msgid "Configuring the Slide Show Settings"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2023(para)
msgid ""
"To start the slide show select <emphasis role=\"strong\">Slide "
"Show</emphasis> from the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Slide Show</emphasis> "
"menu or press <emphasis role=\"strong\">F5</emphasis>."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2029(emphasis)
msgid "Starting the Slide Show"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2042(para)
msgid ""
"The presentation can be viewed as a running slide show. When you reach the "
"last slide of the presentation, you are prompted to exit the presentation by "
"clicking once. However, you can exit a slide show at any point of time by "
"pressing <emphasis role=\"strong\">ESC</emphasis>."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2050(para)
msgid ""
"You can choose to print your slides with notes, as an outline, with page "
"numbers, with date and time and so on. To do this, select <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Print</emphasis> from the <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">File</emphasis> menu."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2056(emphasis)
msgid "Printing the Presentation"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2069(para)
msgid ""
"You can use the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Print</emphasis> dialogue box to "
"further define printer settings or accept the default settings, and click "
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">OK</emphasis> to start printing your presentation."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2075(emphasis)
msgid "Defining Printer Settings"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2089(title)
msgid "Animating Objects and 3D Objects"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2091(para)
msgid "To create a presentation with 3D effects and animations:"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2094(para)
msgid ""
"Open a new presentation in which you want to use 3D graphics and animations, "
"and select a suitable template from the Master pages panel. Now, you can "
"start adding elements to your presentation to spice it up. Begin with "
"placing the title of your presentation on the first slide."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2100(para)
msgid ""
"To create an eye-catching display for the title text, you can use one of the "
"many wonderful text tools available in Impress. One of these is Fontwork, "
"which enables you to create special 3D effects to your text. To start using "
"Fontwork, on the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Drawing</emphasis> toolbar, click "
"the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Fontwork Gallery</emphasis> button. The "
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">Fontwork Gallery</emphasis> window appears."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2109(emphasis)
msgid "Opening Fontwork Gallery"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2122(para)
msgid ""
"Select the style in which you want the title text to be displayed, and click "
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">OK.</emphasis>"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2126(emphasis)
msgid "Selecting a Fontwork Style"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2139(para)
msgid ""
"The text <emphasis role=\"strong\">Fontwork,</emphasis> in the selected "
"style, appears on the slide as an object. To display the title text in place "
"of the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Fontwork</emphasis> object, double-click "
"the object and type the title text in place of the black Fontwork that "
"appears over the object. Click outside the object's selected area to exit "
"the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Fontwork</emphasis> edit mode."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2148(emphasis)
msgid "Editing the Fontwork Object"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2161(para)
msgid ""
"You can go ahead and do the same on the other slides too by inserting 3D "
"images and animating them."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2165(emphasis)
msgid "The 3D Text"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2177(para)
msgid ""
"You can insert 3D graphic objects in your presentation from the 3D-Objects "
"toolbar. By default, this toolbar is not displayed on the Drawing toolbar. "
"To display the 3D-Objects toolbar, on the <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">View</emphasis> menu, point to <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Toolbars</emphasis> and then click <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">3D-Objects</emphasis>."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2185(emphasis)
msgid "Inserting 3D Graphics"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2199(para)
msgid ""
"You can also display the 3D-Objects toolbar by clicking the small arrow at "
"the end of the Drawing toolbar and selecting it from the Visible Buttons "
"list."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2206(para)
msgid ""
"The <emphasis role=\"strong\">3D-Objects toolbar</emphasis> appears as a "
"floating toolbar. If you do not like floating toolbars, you can place it on "
"one of the existing toolbars. To dock the <emphasis role=\"strong\">3D-"
"Objects toolbar</emphasis>, drag the title bar of the toolbar to the desired "
"location and release the mouse button."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2214(emphasis)
msgid "The 3D-Objects Toolbar"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2227(para)
msgid ""
"The <emphasis role=\"strong\">3D-Objects toolbar</emphasis> is now attached "
"to the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Line and Filling toolbar</emphasis>. You "
"can pick up objects from this toolbar and insert them into your slides. To "
"insert a 3D Object on your current slide, click the desired object on the 3 "
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">D-Objects toolbar</emphasis>. Then, move your "
"mouse to the point where you want to insert the object. You can see a plus "
"sign in place of the mouse tip. Holding down the left mouse button, drag the "
"mouse to insert the object on the slide. The selected 3D object appears on "
"the slide."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2239(emphasis)
msgid "Inserting a 3D Object"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2252(para)
msgid ""
"You can change the proportion and size of the object by holding the green "
"handles that appear around it. Impress also provides you tools to apply a "
"number of 3D effects on the object to modify its look and feel as per your "
"requirements. To apply 3D effects on the inserted graphic, right-click the "
"object. On the short-cut menu, click <emphasis role=\"strong\">3D "
"Effects</emphasis>. The <emphasis role=\"strong\">3D Effects</emphasis> "
"dialogue box opens."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2262(emphasis)
msgid "Applying 3D Effects"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2275(para)
msgid ""
"You can use the options available under the different buttons in this "
"dialogue box to define the look and feel of the inserted object. Click the "
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">Illumination</emphasis> button to fine- tune the "
"illumination effect on the object. You can select the appropriate options "
"from the drop-down lists to render the desired illumination effect to the "
"object. Alternatively, you can simply drag the white dot in the graphic at "
"the bottom of the dialogue box and move it to get the desired effect."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2286(para)
msgid ""
"After specifying the desired options, click the <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Assign</emphasis> icon on the top right of the dialogue box "
"to apply the effects on the selected object. Click <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Close</emphasis> to exit the <emphasis role=\"strong\">3D "
"Effects</emphasis> dialogue box."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2293(emphasis)
msgid "Defining 3D Effects"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2307(emphasis)
msgid ""
"If you have enough time, you can also demonstrate the procedure of "
"converting 2D objects into 3D objects and applying the finer 3D effects to "
"it."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2314(para)
msgid ""
"Notice that with a couple of mouse clicks, the 3D object takes on a "
"completely new look. In a similar fashion, you can add many more 3D and 2D "
"elements to your presentation and apply various 3D effects to jazz it up. "
"Impress also offers some animation functionality to help you bring life to "
"your presentations. To display the animation options available in Impress, "
"on the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Slide Show</emphasis> menu, click <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Custom Animation</emphasis>."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2323(para)
msgid ""
"The <emphasis role=\"strong\">Custom Animations</emphasis> panel now appears "
"on the right edge of the presentation window."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2327(emphasis)
msgid "Applying Custom Animation"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2340(para)
msgid ""
"To apply an animation effect on an individual element in your slide, select "
"that element and click the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Add </emphasis> button "
"on the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Custom Animation</emphasis> panel. The "
"Custom Animation dialogue box opens."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2347(emphasis)
msgid "Animating Objects"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2360(para)
msgid ""
"You can now apply various animations to the selected object, define the "
"entrance and exit animation for it and chart a motion path for the object. "
"Similarly, you can specify animation effects for other elements on the "
"slides."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2365(para)
msgid ""
"After defining all the desired settings for the object, click <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">OK </emphasis> to apply the animation effects."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2370(emphasis)
msgid "Customising Animation Effects"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2383(para)
msgid ""
"The specified animations can be viewed at the bottom of the <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Custom Animations</emphasis> panel. You can now view the "
"animation effects in a slide show. Click the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Slide "
"Show</emphasis> button to view the presentation as a slide show."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2390(emphasis)
msgid "Launching a Slide Show"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2403(para)
msgid "Your presentation runs as a spectacular and lively slide show."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2407(emphasis)
msgid "The spectacular Slide Show"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2421(title) chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2438(title)
msgid "Exporting a Presentation"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2423(para)
msgid ""
"As stated earlier, another useful feature associated with Impress is that it "
"has the built-in capacity to export presentations directly into several "
"other file formats. As a result, Impress allows you to export your slide "
"shows directly as Flash (SWF) files."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2430(title)
msgid "To export your presentation as an SWF file:"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2433(para)
msgid ""
"On the <emphasis role=\"strong\">File</emphasis> menu, click <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Export.</emphasis> This opens the <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Export</emphasis> dialogue box."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2450(para)
msgid ""
"Here, you need to specify a file name in the <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Name</emphasis> field and navigate to the directory where "
"you want to export the file. To export the presentation as a Flash file, "
"select <emphasis role=\"strong\">Macromedia Flash (SWF) (.swf)</emphasis> "
"from the file type drop-down list and click <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Save</emphasis>. The file is exported to the indicated "
"location. You can now view the presentation as a Flash file."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2460(title)
msgid "Exporting Presentation as a Flash File"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2475(title)
msgid "Using OpenOffice.org Draw"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2477(para)
msgid ""
"Draw is a vector graphics drawing tool that enables you to create simple and "
"complex drawings and export them in a number of common image formats. Draw "
"also allows you to insert tables, charts, formulas and other items created "
"in OpenOffice.org programmes into your drawings."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2485(para)
msgid ""
"Graphics that are created using a vector graphics drawing tool do not blur "
"when resized."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2489(para)
msgid ""
"Draw is integrated with the OpenOffice.org suite, making it easy toexchange "
"of graphics with other components of the suite. For example, if you create "
"an image in Draw, reusing it in Writer is as simple as copying and pasting "
"the image. A subset of the functions in Draw are also available in Writer "
"and Impress, so you do not have to switch back and forth between them and "
"Draw to perform basic image manipulations."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2497(title)
msgid "Key Features of OpenOffice.org Draw"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2502(para)
msgid ""
"Vector drawing software follows a common notation for referring to all "
"shapes, whether simple lines, rectangles or more complicated shapes, as "
"objects."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2512(title)
msgid "Vector Graphics Creation"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2514(para)
msgid ""
": You can create vector graphics in Draw by using the lines and curves "
"defined by mathematical vectors. Vectors describe lines, ellipses and "
"polygons according to their geometry."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2523(title)
msgid "3D Objects Creation"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2525(para)
msgid ""
": In Draw, you can create simple 3D objects, such as cubes, spheres and "
"cylinders, and modify the light source of the objects."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2533(title)
msgid "Grids and Guides:"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2535(para)
msgid ""
"You can align objects in your drawing by using grids and guides as visual "
"cues. You can also snap an object to a grid line, a guide or to the edge of "
"another object."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2543(title)
msgid "Connecting Objects to Show Relationships:"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2545(para)
msgid ""
"You can attach objects to each other using special lines called connectors "
"to show the relationship between those objects. Connectors attach to glue "
"points on drawing objects and remain attached when those objects move. These "
"are useful for creating things like organisation charts and technical "
"diagrams."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2556(title)
msgid "Displaying Dimensions:"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2558(para)
msgid ""
"You can use dimension lines to calculate and display linear dimensions in "
"technical diagrams, which often show the dimensions of the objects in the "
"drawing."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2566(title)
msgid "Gallery:"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2568(para)
msgid ""
"You can insert and use images, animations, sounds and other items from the "
"OpenOffice.org gallery in your drawings as well as in other OpenOffice.org "
"programmes."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2576(title)
msgid "Graphic File Formats:"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2578(para)
msgid ""
"Export your creation to many common graphic file formats, such as BMP, GIF, "
"JPG and PNG."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2507(para)
msgid ""
"Draw provides extensive functionality that integrates more functions than "
"the majority of drawing tools available in office suites. Some of the key "
"features of Draw are: <placeholder-1/>"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2586(title)
msgid "Performing Basic Drawing Operations"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2589(title)
msgid "To launch OpenOffice.org Draw:"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2592(para)
msgid ""
"On the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Applications</emphasis> menu, select "
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">Graphics</emphasis> and then <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">OpenOffice.org Drawing</emphasis>."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2594(para)
msgid ""
"The main components of the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Draw</emphasis> window "
"are shown in the following graphic:"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2599(title)
msgid "The Draw Window"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2611(para)
msgid ""
"The drawings are created in the drawing area, which is surrounded by the "
"following toolbars:"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2616(para)
msgid ""
"The <emphasis role=\"strong\">Menu</emphasis> bar lists the main menus "
"available in Draw. It includes options to manage, edit and view the format "
"of your drawings."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2622(para)
msgid ""
"The <emphasis role=\"strong\">Function</emphasis> bar displays icons to "
"perform tasks such as Open, Save, Copy, Cut and Paste."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2628(para)
msgid ""
"The <emphasis role=\"strong\">Line and Filling</emphasis> bar includes "
"specific drawing tools to modify the appearance of a selected object such as "
"line style, colour and thickness; fill style and colour."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2635(para)
msgid ""
"The <emphasis role=\"strong\">Drawing</emphasis> toolbar is the most "
"important toolbar in Draw. It contains all the necessary functions for "
"drawing various geometric and freehand shapes. Creating basic shapes in Draw "
"requires the extensive use of this toolbar. However, you have to further "
"edit, combine and manipulate them to create complex objects."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2642(para)
msgid ""
"You can vary the number and position of the visible tools to make the "
"interface look a bit different. To add or remove a toolbar from the Draw "
"window:"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2650(para)
msgid ""
"On the <emphasis role=\"strong\">View</emphasis> menu, point to <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Toolbars.</emphasis> The <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Toolbar</emphasis> list displays the toolbars available, "
"with a check mark next to the toolbars that are displayed. To remove a "
"toolbar from the Draw window, clear the corresponding check mark and click "
"the toolbar without a check mark to add it to the window."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2661(title)
msgid "Creating Objects"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2663(para)
msgid "To create an object by using the Drawing toolbar:"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2666(para)
msgid ""
"Click a specific object button such as <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Rectangle</emphasis> or <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Ellipse</emphasis> on the <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Drawing</emphasis> toolbar, and place the mouse cursor at "
"the point in the drawing area where you want the object to start."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2675(para)
msgid ""
"Press the left button on the mouse, drag the cursor to where you want the "
"object to end and release the button. The object appears in the Drawing area."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2684(para)
msgid ""
"The Drawing toolbar is not discussed in detail because you use its options "
"to draw only basic shapes. For novice users, demonstrate the creation of a "
"few objects, such as square, rectangle and connector. Visit <ulink "
"url=\"http://documentation.openoffice.org/\">http://documentation.openoffice."
"org/</ulink> for more details on OpenOfice.org products."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2693(title)
msgid "Selecting Objects"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2695(para)
msgid ""
"Before making any changes to an object, you need to select the object. Draw "
"provides the following options to select an object:"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2702(para)
msgid "Direct Selection: Click the object to select it."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2706(para)
msgid ""
"Selection by Framing: On the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Drawing</emphasis> "
"toolbar, click the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Select</emphasis> button and "
"drag a large rectangle around the object to select it. This option is useful "
"for selecting multiple objects in the drawing area."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2715(para)
msgid ""
"You have to enclose the object(s) completely in the rectangle to select them."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2720(title)
msgid "Selecting by Framing"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2732(para)
msgid ""
"Selecting hidden objects: To select an object that is covered by another "
"object, press Alt key and click the object you want to select."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2739(para)
msgid ""
"To be able to select a hidden object, you must know the position of that "
"object relative to the objects on top."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2746(title)
msgid "Editing Objects"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2748(para)
msgid ""
"When creating objects, you may have to edit them or change their properties "
"to get the desired output. However, you may not always find that flexibility "
"in the default software settings. For example, you cannot change the shape "
"of the square to a rectangle or rotate the square on its own axis by using "
"the default <emphasis role=\"strong\">Drawing</emphasis> toolbar. To perform "
"these tasks, Draw provides various other options with the required "
"flexibility, such as:"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2761(para)
msgid ""
"All the options covered in the subsequent sections apply to a selected "
"object or a group of objects. You can identify a selected object from any "
"other by the small, coloured square or circle around the object. These "
"squares or circles are called handles and form a rectangular frame that is "
"just big enough to contain the object."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2770(title)
msgid "Modifying Object Size"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2773(para)
msgid ""
"In the Drawing area, select the created object by clicking it. Handles "
"appear on the object."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2777(emphasis)
msgid "Selecting an Object"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2790(para)
msgid ""
"Place the mouse cursor over one of the handles. When the cursor becomes a "
"double-headed arrow, drag the cursor in the direction of the arrow to modify "
"the size of the object. If you choose a corner handle, you will resize the "
"object along two axes at the same time. If you use a side handle, the "
"objects will only be resized along one axis. The outline of the resulting "
"new object appears as a dotted line."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2800(para)
msgid ""
"Release the mouse button when the object is sized correctly. The dotted line "
"disappears, and the resized object appears."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2804(emphasis)
msgid "Modifying the Object"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2818(title)
msgid "Arranging Objects"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2820(para)
msgid ""
"If the document you are working on includes many overlapping objects, "
"editing of individual objects (which may or may not be visible) might pose a "
"challenge. Fortunately, Draw provides a way to rearrange objects without "
"affecting their layout."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2827(title)
msgid "To change the arrangement of objects:"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2830(para)
msgid ""
"In the drawing area, right-click the object you want to rearrange, point to "
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">Arrange</emphasis> and select the appropriate "
"option from the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Arrange</emphasis> list."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2836(title)
msgid "Rearranging the Object"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2848(para)
msgid ""
"If you select the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Send Backward</emphasis> option, "
"the output is as shown in the following graphic:"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2853(title)
msgid "Object Sent Backwards"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2866(para)
msgid ""
"If time permits, ask the students to explore the other options in the "
"Arrange list. In addition, explain which option to use under what "
"circumstances. Specifically discuss the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Behind "
"Object</emphasis> option and the difference between the output from the "
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">Send to Back</emphasis> and <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Behind Object</emphasis> options. This is a low-priority "
"activity."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2878(title) chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2903(title)
msgid "Duplicating Objects"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2880(para)
msgid ""
"Often, you may need to create multiple objects of the same shape and size. "
"In Draw, you can duplicate or make multiple copies of an object. The copies "
"can be identical or differ in size, colour, orientation and location."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2887(title)
msgid "To create multiple copies of an object:"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2890(para)
msgid ""
"Click the object to be copied, click <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Edit</emphasis> and select the <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Duplicate</emphasis> option. The <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Duplicate</emphasis> dialogue box opens."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2897(para)
msgid ""
"Specify the appropriate values in the <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Duplicate</emphasis> dialogue box, and click <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">OK</emphasis> to display the output in the drawing area."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2916(title)
msgid "Grouping and Combining Objects"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2918(para)
msgid ""
"When creating or editing an object, the object might be displaced from its "
"original position. This change in location disturbs the relative position of "
"the object to the others in the drawing. This could be critical where "
"accuracy, in terms of position, is important such as in architectural "
"drawings. Using Draw, you can combine drawing objects in two distinct ways, "
"grouping and combining."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2927(title)
msgid "Grouping Objects"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2929(para)
msgid ""
"Grouping objects is like putting them into a container, where the objects "
"are grouped with each other but retain their individual identities. You can "
"move the group as one entity and apply changes to all the enclosed objects. "
"A group can always be undone, and the objects that constitute the group can "
"always be manipulated separately."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2938(title)
msgid "To group objects:"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2941(para)
msgid ""
"In the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Drawing</emphasis> area, select all the "
"objects you want to include in the group. Right click any selected object, "
"and then select the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Group</emphasis> option."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2948(para)
msgid ""
"Click any object in the group; handles appear around the entire group "
"instead of around an object."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2956(para)
msgid ""
"Place the mouse cursor over one of the handles. When the cursor becomes a "
"double-headed arrow, drag the cursor to increase or decrease the size of the "
"objects in the group. All the objects in the group are resized equally."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2953(para)
msgid ""
"You can now modify the entire group, without applying effects to objects "
"individually. To resize a group: <placeholder-1/>"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2964(title)
msgid ""
"You can also edit a single object in the group without breaking it. To edit "
"individual objects in a group:"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2968(para)
msgid ""
"Double-click an object in the group. You can now enter the group and work on "
"individual objects."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2973(para)
msgid ""
"Click the object you want to edit; the handles appear around that object. In "
"this mode, you can edit, add or delete this object."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2979(para)
msgid ""
"To re-instate the group after modifying the object, double-click anywhere "
"outside the selection frame."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2987(para)
msgid ""
"You can group objects of all shapes and sizes. You can group objects in 2D, "
"3D or a combination of both. However, you can combine only overlapping 2D "
"objects."
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2993(title) chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:3018(title)
msgid "Combining Objects"
msgstr ""

#: chapter4/Using_OpenOffice_Applications.xml:2995(para)
msgid ""
